original_title: Se parhaiten nauraa, joka viimeksi nauraa
overview: Martti Vaara, secondary school graduate gets monetary help from his rich uncle under the pretense to get married and have kids. When the uncle unexpectedly arrives to look at the little one, Martti persuades his friends to get involved on the hoax.
title: Se parhaiten nauraa, joka viimeksi nauraa
